description: Demolition of the existing 72 bed care home and redevelopment to provide a part three/part four storey building consisting of a 64 bed care home, 16 independent living suites and 48 independent living flats together with communal facilities (to include a synagogue, day centre, restaurant, activity rooms, gym, shops and guest facilities); provision of new outbuildings along the northern boundary including a substation and generator; provision of vehicular and cycle parking together with internal access arrangement works; provision of refuse storage and associated landscape and tree works within the site.
